commitResults.messageBody:
The list of participants for a meeting is not updated even when the
corresponding contact is deleted.

This is problematic as the user needs to manually edit the meeting after
deleting a contact to update the participant list.

Let's enhance the delete contact feature so that deleting a contact
automatically updates the participant list of affected meetings.

commitResults.messageTitle: Fix regressions from enhancing delete contact

commitResults.messageBody:
The list of participants for a meeting is not updated even when the
corresponding contact is edited, so the information displayed in the
meeting's participant list may not always be accurate.

Let's enhance the update contact feature so that editing a contact
automatically updates the participant list of affected meetings.
